<!--
    Telugu (తెలుగు) — te
    Script : Telugu script; LTR.  Rendered via Noto Sans Telugu (bundled API 21+).
    Approx.: ~83 M L1 speakers (Andhra Pradesh, Telangana/India; diaspora).
    Register: Standard Modern Telugu (ఆధునిక వ్యవహారిక తెలుగు) as used in
              formal writing and broadcast media.
    Notes  : Telugu is an abugida; Android's ICU handles conjuncts correctly.
             Three grammatical genders (masculine, feminine, neuter).  Polite
             second-person pronoun మీరు used throughout UI.
             "Binge drinking" → అతిగా మద్యపానం చేయడం.
    Source : Translated from values-de/strings.xml (German source of truth).
-->
